陵南站，看后续能否改进。湖南一火车站不让进候车厅，乘客顶烈日排队，铁路部门回应 _ 南站 _ 茶陵 _ 时间"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-30b4c0c14a2eb1f33afc210c11006b11_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/610039783"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyZWriMLmjb0BEAMaCDk3ODQ1MTA4IMXniKUGMAA43gJAK3IJNjEwMDM5NzgzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1688504902.852828", "card_id": "Q_609867787", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "都说老潘森的 Q 十分强力，那么和它差不多的老努努 E 和石头人 Q 为什么无法代替潘森？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "老喷森 Q，老努努 E，石头人 Q，都是指定一个目标，单体招式。 老努努 E 和石头人 Q 还有减速。 为何他们无法做到老潘森的 Q（老潘森 Q 无任何额外效果）的压迫感呢？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d587b8eda38a082d7c50c7d01ebf979f_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/609867787"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IyZWriMLmjb0BEAMaCDk3ODA2NzcyIMiZgqUGMAA4IUAscgk2MDk4Njc3ODd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1688504902.853170", "card_id": "Q_606563796", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 71}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "高考后该怎样安排自己的假期生活？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/606563796"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IyZWriMLmjb0BEAMaCDk3MDcyMzIzIJXfpaQGMAA4UkAtcgk2MDY1NjM3OTZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1688504902.85